---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden py-20 sm:py-32">
  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center">
      <!-- Badge -->
      <div class="mb-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full glass-card !rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-emerald-400">
        <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
          <span class="absolute inline-flex h-full w-full animate-ping rounded-full bg-emerald-400 opacity-75"></span>
          <span class="relative inline-flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500"></span>
        </span>
        Chega de ficar preso no WhatsApp
      </div>

      <!-- Headline -->
      <h1 class="mx-auto max-w-4xl text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl">
        Deixe a IA cuidar dos
        <span class="gradient-text">
          agendamentos
        </span>
      </h1>

      <!-- Subheadline -->
      <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg text-slate-400 sm:text-xl">
        Enquanto você está atendendo, a IA responde seus clientes,
        verifica sua agenda e marca os horários. Acabou o "qual horário você tem?"
      </p>

      <!-- CTA Buttons -->
      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:justify-center">
        <a
          href="https://app.zimplou.com"
          class="btn-glass btn-glass-primary text-lg"
        >
          Testar grátis por 10 dias
          <svg class="ml-2 h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a
          href="#how-it-works"
          class="btn-glass btn-glass-secondary"
        >
          <svg class="h-5 w-5 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M14.752 11.168l-3.197-2.132A1 1 0 0010 9.87v4.263a1 1 0 001.555.832l3.197-2.132a1 1 0 000-1.664z" />
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
          Ver como funciona
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Animated Industries Marquee -->
  <div class="mt-20 relative">
    <p class="text-center text-sm text-slate-500 mb-6">Para todo mundo que trabalha com agendamentos</p>

    <!-- Gradient masks -->
    <div class="absolute left-0 top-6 bottom-0 w-24 sm:w-32 bg-gradient-to-r from-slate-950 to-transparent z-10 pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="absolute right-0 top-6 bottom-0 w-24 sm:w-32 bg-gradient-to-l from-slate-950 to-transparent z-10 pointer-events-none"></div>

    <!-- Marquee container -->
    <div class="overflow-hidden">
      <div class="marquee-track">
        <div class="marquee-content">
          {industries.map((industry) => (
            <div class="marquee-item glass-card !rounded-full px-4 py-2 flex items-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap">
              <span class={industry.color} set:html={iconSvgs[industry.icon]} />
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-300">{industry.name}</span>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
        <!-- Duplicate for seamless loop -->
        <div class="marquee-content" aria-hidden="true">
          {industries.map((industry) => (
            <div class="marquee-item glass-card !rounded-full px-4 py-2 flex items-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap">
              <span class={industry.color} set:html={iconSvgs[industry.icon]} />
              <span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-300">{industry.name}</span>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .marquee-track {
    display: flex;
    width: fit-content;
    animation: marquee 45s linear infinite;
  }

  .marquee-content {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding-right: 1rem;
  }

  .marquee-item {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
  }

  .marquee-item:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3);
  }

  @keyframes marquee {
    0% {
      transform: translateX(0);
    }
    100% {
      transform: translateX(-50%);
    }
  }

  /* Pause on hover */
  .marquee-track:hover {
    animation-play-state: paused;
  }
</style>
